DIVIDE AND CONQUER ------- eg - Binary search, merge sort, quick sort,etc
                           use - when we cant use greedy
                           how - recursively
                           
##########STEPS##########                  
-> DIVIDE - break the problem in sub problem until the problem can be solved directly                           PROBLEM
-> RECURSION - recursively solve subproblems                                                                     /   \
-> CONQUER - combine the solutions of sub problem to get the final solution                                     /     \
##########################                                                                                     /        \
                                                                                                        SUB-Problem     SUB-Problem
                                                                                                              |               |
                                                                                                          RECURSIVE         RECURSIVE
                                                                                                        LEAP OF FAITH      LEAP OF FAITH
                                                                                                                |                  |   
                                                                                                                |                  |     
                                                                                                                |__________________|
                                                                                                                           |
                                                                                                                   COMBINE and GET the 
                                                                                                                       ANSWER :-\ XD

